{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji26","name":"毛泽东全集第26卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji26.pdf"],"article":{"title":"复徐向前等电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"复徐向前等电！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年5月3日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）同意你过一时期去海边适当地点作较长时期之休养。（二）同意解除你在十八兵团的工作并在病愈后改做别项工作。（三）同意以周士第为十八兵团司令员兼政委，王新亭为十八兵团副司令员兼副政委。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的复徐向前并告周士第、罗瑞卿、"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":5,"day":3}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":372,"page_end":372},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"徐向前","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}